      "digest": {
        "published": "2025-08-15",
        "description": "The Bit Form builder plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to arbitrary file uploads due to missing file type validation in all versions up to, and including, 2.20.4. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attackers to upload arbitrary files on the affected site's server which may make remote code execution possible. For this to be exploitable, the PRO version needs to be installed and activated as well. Additionally a form with an advanced file upload element needs to be published.",
        "title": "The Bit Form builder plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to arbitrary file uploads due to missing file type validation in all versions up...",
        "attack_type": "RCE",
        "cvss_max": 9.8
      },
      "cve": {
        "id": "CVE-2025-6679",
        "sourceIdentifier": "security@wordfence.com",
        "published": "2025-08-15T07:15:28.600",
        "lastModified": "2026-04-15T00:35:42.020",
        "vulnStatus": "Deferred",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "The Bit Form builder plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to arbitrary file uploads due to missing file type validation in all versions up to, and including, 2.20.4. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attackers to upload arbitrary files on the affected site's server which may make remote code execution possible. For this to be exploitable, the PRO version needs to be installed and activated as well. Additionally a form with an advanced file upload element needs to be published."
          },
          {
            "lang": "es",
            "value": "El complemento Bit Form Builder para WordPress es vulnerable a la carga de archivos arbitrarios debido a la falta de validación del tipo de archivo en todas las versiones hasta la 2.20.4 incluida. Esto permite que atacantes no autenticados carguen archivos arbitrarios en el servidor del sitio afectado, lo que podría posibilitar la ejecución remota de código. Para que esto sea explotable, también es necesario instalar y activar la versión PRO. Además, es necesario publicar un formulario con un elemento avanzado de carga de archivos."
          }
        ],
        "metrics": {
          "cvssMetricV31": [
            {
